00:38:33.360 --> 00:38:34.719
...Ihr Vermögen?

00:38:39.159 --> 00:38:40.000
Was machst du?

00:38:42.719 --> 00:38:43.559
Deine Hand.

00:38:44.039 --> 00:38:44.599
Hand.

